      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/549537968_18518000608020842_7143394985570168982_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcyMzQ5NjYzMjcwMTcwNzU3Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=xSPf9zAPGnoQ7kNvwErRCSA&amp;_nc_oc=Adpg09N7gHj55u_X9gTb4YbFjV5090iw6-xTVYVpxZBfsyZmOTn0gf3IfX8ZrOxfXTg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=vNrRMQqSHXlYAF1toImDEQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxA9H33i-ndtgYuCZvf2vz8cDDa46U-3c4mTbpK6KZ3Yg&amp;oe=69C8C90B" alt="Instagram billede fra @baxterdury" /></p><p><strong>@baxterdury</strong></p><p>What a lovely week so far since releasing Allbarone last Friday, the reviews have been beautiful, @laurenlaverne was the perfect person to talk to and then I was presented with presidential figs in a leather case in my hotel room in Istanbul from the incredibly brave people that run #Eksenonfair. The tour is selling out and the unique @joshuaidehen will be with us the whole way. Xxx<br/>
@heavenlyrecordings</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/549537968_18518000608020842_7143394985570168982_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcyMzQ5NjYzMjcwMTcwNzU3Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=xSPf9zAPGnoQ7kNvwErRCSA&amp;_nc_oc=Adpg09N7gHj55u_X9gTb4YbFjV5090iw6-xTVYVpxZBfsyZmOTn0gf3IfX8ZrOxfXTg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=vNrRMQqSHXlYAF1toImDEQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxA9H33i-ndtgYuCZvf2vz8cDDa46U-3c4mTbpK6KZ3Yg&amp;oe=69C8C90B" alt="Instagram billede fra @baxterdury" /></p><p><strong>@baxterdury</strong></p><p>What a lovely week so far since releasing Allbarone last Friday, the reviews have been beautiful, @laurenlaverne was the perfect person to talk to and then I was presented with presidential figs in a leather case in my hotel room in Istanbul from the incredibly brave people that run #Eksenonfair. The tour is selling out and the unique @joshuaidehen will be with us the whole way. Xxx<br/>
@heavenlyrecordings</p>]]></content:encoded>
